name: spec
description: Generate a PRD, task list, and draft implementation plan for a new feature. Use when starting any non-trivial work that touches more than one file or surface. Enters plan mode and requires explicit approval before writing anything to disk. Triggers for "spec for X", "write a spec", "plan feature X", "I want to build X".
